Package: esim
Version: 1.0.0
Section: electronics
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: OpenAI <noreply@openai.com>
Depends: bash, desktop-file-utils, hicolor-icon-theme, xdg-utils
Description: eSim electronic design automation suite
 eSim is an electronic design automation suite for schematic capture and
 simulation. This Debian package is a packaging scaffold that installs the
 application under /opt/esim and provides a launcher in /usr/bin/esim.
